summary: TL* THE CONTACT OWNS A 2005 TOYOTA SIENNA. WHILE THE REAR PASSENGER ATTEMPTED TO EXIT THE VEHICLE,. THE REAR PASSENGER SIDE SLIDING DOOR FAILED TO FUNCTION. AS A RESULT, THE PASSENGER WAS UNABLE TO EXIT THE VEHICLE. THE VEHICLE WAS NOT DIAGNOSED OR REPAIRED. THE MANUFACTURER WAS NOTIFIED OF THE FAILURE. THE FAILURE MILEAGE WAS 65,000.
